      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DOMINEERING (6) is a smart dog who ran the fastest time on the card last time scoring by 1.3 lengths (18.13) at this track. Superior out of the boxes and will be in the firing line early. Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. In top form and looks a key chance again. KILCOY TIGER (7) flew the lids and led throughout to get off the mark with his maiden win, then finished a 5.5 lengths sixth last start at Richmond Straight over 324m (18.09). Maiden this journey but has some solid runs behind him. Well placed here and should do much better. ROSACKY SKY (5) hasn't been far away, finishing in the money twice in a row including last time in a Grade 5 at this track over 320m. Can hit the frame this time. WOOPI EXPRESS (2) is one of the chances after collecting a minor prize last time.",
